the common fixed points of `veblenWith f o'` over all\n  `o' < o`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/SetTheory/Ordinal/Veblen.html#Ordinal.veblenWith","kind":"def","line":58,"name":"Ordinal.veblenWith","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/SetTheory/Ordinal/Veblen.lean#L58-L68"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.SetTheory.Ordinal.FixedPoint"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.SetTheory.Ordinal.Veblen"}